explain: If a student makes an error in Sentence_Reading, there is a high probability of making an error in Paragraph_Reading as well (confidence=0.85, lift=1.46).
If a student makes an error in Word_Usage, there is a high probability of making an error in Sentence_Reading as well (confidence=0.72, lift=1.25).
If a student makes an error in Paragraph_Structure, there is a high probability of making an error in Paragraph_Reading as well (confidence=0.68, lift=1.20).
If a student makes an error in Word_Recognition, there is a high probability of making an error in Word_Usage as well (confidence=0.60, lift=1.15).
